<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>343</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǎng tú bá shè shí yào yǒu shǒu yǔ shǒu de chān fú
 huàn nán tòng kǔ shí yào yǒu xīn yǔ xīn de kào lǒng
 zhè jiù shì bǐ cǐ xiāng ài zhè jiù shì shén de mìng lìng
 jǔ mù kàn tiān kōng tuán jié de yàn zhèn nǐ hái yǒu shén me bù dǒng
 hé yī xiāng ài yǒng yuǎn dōu shì shén de mìng lìng
 shéi zài shén jiā quán rán jǐn zhōng shéi jiù shì wǒ qīn ài de dì xiōng.</lyrics>
<title>hé yī xiāng ài 迦南343</title>
</song>